diff --git a/HAL_ISSUE_LOG.md b/HAL_ISSUE_LOG.md
index 0f28e2d..b755183 100644
--- a/HAL_ISSUE_LOG.md
+++ b/HAL_ISSUE_LOG.md
@@ -140,3 +140,66 @@
   - `AA BB CC DD EE`
   - `AA BB CC DD EE FF 11`
   - `AA BB CC DD EE FF 11 22`
